::DeathStorm/Zardus::

DeathStorm takes in a breath of pain as the dagger digs into his stomach. The 
assassin falls to the ground, clutching at his stomach and going unconscious.

Zardus grins, taking a few steps forward. "Excelent. Nemesis and Scattershot, 
stand down. Nemesis, take him to the lab. I want you to extract his spark and 
give it to me. One that is done, you two can do whatever you please with his 
body."
